<h1>Pingry COVID Update</h1>
<h2>Notice of transfer to isolation protocol.</h2>
<hr/>

<p>Dear <%= "#{@student.last_name}" %> Family,</p>

<p>According to Pingry's official COVID-19 database, <%= @student.first_name %> has just received a presumed or confirmed diagnosis of COVID-19. This email represents your confirmation that <%= @student.first_name %> is being transferred from quarantine to isolation protocol.</p>

<p>During the isolation, <%= @student.first_name %> will not be permitted on any Pingry campus. If <%= @student.first_name %> feels capable of taking courses, they may engage with coursework through the flexible virtual learning model established by Pingry Anywhere. If <%= @student.first_name %> has any updates to their isolation status, please contact <a href="mailto:ecarannante@pingry.org">Erin Carannante</a>. You should be receiving an additional email shortly confirming the start of the isolation period. Thank you for your help in keeping Pingry safe, and best wishes for a speedy recovery!</p>


